<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/series/court-statistics-quarterly">Court statistics quarterly</a></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/gender-recognition-certificate-statistics">Gender recognition certificate statistics</a></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/series/judicial-and-court-statistics">Judicial and court statistics</a></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/local-adult-reoffending">Local adult reoffending statistics</a></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/new-criminal-offences-statistics">New criminal offences statistics</a></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/series/probation-service-workforce-quarterly-reports">Probation Service workforce quarterly reports</a></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/series/statistics-on-privacy-injunctions">Statistics on privacy injunctions</a></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice/series/statistics-on-the-use-of-language-services-in-courts-and-tribunals">Statistics on the use of language services in the courts and tribunals</a></p>

<p>Ministry of Justice statistics before 2013 can be found on the <a rel="external" href="http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20130315183909/http://www.justice.gov.uk/statistics">The National Archives website</a>.</p>

